extends java.lang.Object
implements Visitor<E,F,D>

Implements the depth first traversal of the AST. Each node is visited once for each parent. That is, if a node has exactly one parent, it is visited exactly once. If it is status by two parents, it is visited twice, following each of the parents' child pointers.
